HEADWORD: Antilogy
<hw>An*til"o*gy</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧n*t⟦icr⟧l"⟦osl⟧*j⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Antilogies</plw>
